{"tid":948691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人大教授向松祚引述官方內部消息    中國今年實際經濟增長只1.67","createTime":"2018-12-20T09:03:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-24T03:50:29.000Z","uid":184679,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"788e4597a87578635ed3e714dbeefcaa3bd2f636","tid":948691,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T09:03:48.000Z","msg":"紐約時報報道，人民大學教授、國際貨幣研究所理事兼副所長向松祚在早前上海舉行的論壇表示，他從一個官方機關的研究員得知，中國今年經濟增長真實數字只是1.67，或許會更低。<br />\n<br />\n這個預測是多個經濟專家們推測的數字中，位於最低者。紐時指出，但是中國的經濟增長，普遍被外界認為要比官方數字要低，而今年官方的數字是6.5%。<br />\n<br />\n紐時又報道，雖然習近平在演說中列舉很多數據，證明改革開放的成就，包括數千年來中國人民飽受饑餓、糧食短缺和貧窮，已經大致上遠離我們。但目前跡象顯示，政府正在加強管制地方經濟數據的發布，上個月，中國最富有省份之一的廣東省，就突然停止公布每月經理採購指數。這個數據可以測量中國重要的製造業體溫。據稱廣東省是因應國家統計局的要求而停止發布上述數據。統計局聲稱，廣東省曾經違規彙集統計數據。<br />\n<br />\n中國過去也曾禁止發表經濟數據，包括2015年10月的財新經理採購指數、12月的民新經理採購指數、2016年1月的外彙購買指數、12月中國地產指數、2018年1月固定資產投資指數以及今年6月海關出口領先指數。不約而同，被禁止發表的數據，幾乎都反映了經濟情況下滑的情況。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://trad.cn.rfi.fr/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20181220-%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%A7%E6%95%99%E6%8E%88%E5%90%91%E6%9D%BE%E7%A5%9A%E5%BC%95%E8%BF%B0%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E5%85%A7%E9%83%A8%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E5%AF%A6%E9%9A%9B%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E5%A2%9E%E9%95%B7%E5%8F%AA167\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftrad.cn.rfi.fr%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F20181220-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2595%2599%25E6%258E%2588%25E5%2590%2591%25E6%259D%25BE%25E7%25A5%259A%25E5%25BC%2595%25E8%25BF%25B0%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%2585%25A7%25E9%2583%25A8%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF%25E4%25BB%258A%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%25E5%25A2%259E%25E9%2595%25B7%25E5%258F%25AA167&d=JToigBLEqFuBXABKqoXuzIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=a1815379\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://trad.cn.rfi.fr/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20181220-%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%A7%E6%95%99%E6%8E%88%E5%90%91%E6%9D%BE%E7%A5%9A%E5%BC%95%E8%BF%B0%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E5%85%A7%E9%83%A8%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E5%AF%A6%E9%9A%9B%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E5%A2%9E%E9%95%B7%E5%8F%AA167</a>"},{"pid":"7c683b6341dbc73b2ad2bb952a22fcc0c4bd717e","tid":948691,"uid":39653,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T09:05:42.000Z","msg":"真.克強指數<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07af824ae35eacef123cac00d31f6e337993e223","tid":948691,"uid":184679,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T09:11:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://lianghui.people.com.cn/NMediaFile/2016/0317/MAIN201603170748000467407273893.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flianghui.people.com.cn%2FNMediaFile%2F2016%2F0317%2FMAIN201603170748000467407273893.jpg&h=ece8a782&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"595cfeaa682fefb13a64910f748fe1b03eda63bc","tid":948691,"uid":31237,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T09:11:59.000Z","msg":"一碌柒"},{"pid":"4af200c0e17197105ac51f83a57f6b19a78fd78c","tid":948691,"uid":61280,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T09:14:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">負數我就會信DD囉！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"107918b72c95b36724d79bc26e726433ef8b3c4b","tid":948691,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T09:17:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/Trlp4CNIPcg/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FTrlp4CNIPcg%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=d8f1dc84&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dc1a2a31d0468e34bf82d3514c5f273be15f3fa0","tid":948691,"uid":49609,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T09:18:01.000Z","msg":"167<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c815aa71f6d2cd2cfb0eb96d59596bb142768bdb","tid":948691,"uid":511,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid"